Step to run application

1) Clone this repo
2) Run 'npm install'
3) Edit .env file and set appropriate values for your MongoDB installation
4) Run 'npm start'
5) Point your browser to http://localhost:3000

Available routes

/business 
	GET A list of 20 random businesses sorted by name
/business/:business_id 
	GET Details for a given business_id along with its associated reviews
/facets
	GET Facet output by categories, stars, and price range
